Subject: RIPEM 1.3A1

An early test version of Jeff's mods to RIPEM is now available
on ripem.msu.edu.  The filename is ripem1.3a1.zip, and it is
in directory /pub/crypt/ripem/experimental.

I have not completed merging in the other recent mods made in parallel
with Jeff, and the makefile supports only Unix platforms (& I
have tested only the Sun).  (Since Jeff develops under DOS,
I am surprised he's updated the Unix makefile but not the 
DOS one.  Maybe he's running Linux these days?)

This early version is for those who are anxious to look at
Jeff's new RIPEM API.

Mark
